OL,3,CUK's oldest cinema, The Electric,
OL,4,Ccloses after 114 years
OL,6,FThe UK's oldest working cinema, The
OL,7,FElectric in , has closed after 114
OL,8,Fyears.
OL,10,FA source said the historic picture
OL,11,Fhouse had shut down on Friday 29
OL,12,FFebruary, for the 'foreseeable future.'
OL,14,FA petition, currently signed by 2,200
OL,15,Fpeople, has been launched to save the
OL,16,Fhistoric venue.
OL,18,FThe Electric - which opened on Station
OL,19,FStreet in December 1909 - reopened
OL,20,Fafter the pandemic under new
OL,21,Fmanagement in 2022.
