OL,3,CUK's oldest cinema, The Electric,
OL,4,Ccloses after 114 years
OL,6,FIt's believed an 88-year lease for the
OL,7,Fbuilding comes to an end this month,
OL,8,Falongside unconfirmed speculation that
OL,9,Fa property developer intends to seek
OL,10,Fplanning permission to build flats on
OL,11,Fthe site.
OL,13,FThere are no upcoming film showings
OL,14,Flisted on the venue's website.
OL,16,FThe organisers of the city's Flatpack
OL,17,FFestival said this year's event would
OL,18,Ftake place without The Electric as a
OL,19,Fvenue for the first time in 18 years.
