OL,3,CUK's oldest cinema, The Electric,
OL,4,Ccloses after 114 years
OL,6,FThe cinema reopened its doors in
OL,7,FJanuary 2022, having been closed since
OL,8,FMarch 2020.
OL,10,FIt is currently owned by Kevin
OL,11,FMarkwick, who also owns the 104-year-
OL,12,Fold Picture House Cinema in Uckfield,
OL,13,FEast Sussex, and was run by his
OL,14,Fdaughter, Katie Markwick.
OL,16,FThe Electric has been contacted for
OL,17,Fcomment.
